What about my computer?

17
00:01:51,340 --> 00:01:54,174
那個 網絡攝像頭還是什麼的
The... the webcam or whatever it's called.

18
00:01:54,176 --> 00:01:56,843
我是說 他們能不能黑進去
I mean, c-can't they hack into that

