689
00:29:14,307 --> 00:29:17,075
你偷了你父親的槍
You stole your father's guns.

690
00:29:17,077 --> 00:29:19,243
兩個夥伴被殺了
Two of your friends were killed,

691
00:29:19,245 --> 00:29:20,979
你差點兒被殺
you were nearly killed,

692
00:29:20,981 --> 00:29:24,115
