and you won't cooperate with us?

693
00:29:24,117 --> 00:29:26,517
你以為你是誰
Who do you think you are?

694
00:29:26,519 --> 00:29:28,987
這不重要 你不會相信我
Doesn't matter, you won't believe me.

695
00:29:28,989 --> 00:29:31,489
試試看
Try me.

696
00:29:33,293 --> 00:29:37,161
Emma和我幾年前去過蘇丹的城市Jo
Emma and I visited Jo in Sudan a couple of years ago.

697
00:29:37,163 --> 00:29:39,030
我們都很震驚
We were shocked.

698
00:29:39,032 --> 00:29:41,232
那兒和這兒有天壤之別
It couldn't have been more different than here--

699
