but then Boko Haram attacked.

704
00:29:55,682 --> 00:29:57,448
我們逃到大使館
We were whisked

705
00:29:57,450 --> 00:30:00,284
尋求庇護 但是
into the embassy for safety, but...

706
00:30:00,286 --> 00:30:04,622
我們通過大門看到不斷發生的襲擊
we watched the attack keep happening through the gates.

707
00:30:06,092 --> 00:30:08,459
但是沒人想去阻止
And nobody tried to stop it.

708
00:30:09,729 --> 00:30:12,363
女人被強暴
Women being raped,

709
00:30:12,365 --> 00:30:14,532
孩子被射殺
children being shot.

710
00:30:15,902 --> 00:30:18,236
我們卻無能為力
And there was nothing we could do.

711
00:30:20,106 --> 00:30:23,041
你不可能忘記這些事
You don't ever unsee something like that.

712
00:30:26,846 --> 00:30:29,047
槍是給村民的
Guns are for the villagers.

713
00:30:30,283 --> 00:30:31,949
用來保護自己
To protect themselves.

714
00:30:31,951 --> 00:30:33,718
因為沒有人會保護他們
'Cause nobody else will.

715
00:30:33,720 --> 00:30:36,154
但博科聖地一定是發現了
But Boko Haram must've found out

716
00:30:36,156 --> 00:30:37,255
我們做的事
what we've been doing,

717
00:30:37,257 --> 00:30:39,123
所以他們來到這裏 要阻止我們
so they came here to try and stop us.

718
00:30:39,125 --> 00:30:41,459
這是個崇高的動機
It's a noble cause,

719
00:30:41,461 --> 00:30:44,896
但這是完全違法的
but it's-it's completely illegal.

720
00:30:44,898 --> 00:30:47,065
偷槍
Stealing guns,

721
00:30:47,067 --> 00:30:50,601
走私到海外
smuggling them out of the country...

722
00:30:50,603 --> 00:30:54,672
違反了15條聯邦法律 你是知道的
breaks 15 federal laws, you know that.

723
00:30:56,276 --> 00:30:59,677
