不把槍給村民
get the villagers those guns...

727
00:31:09,389 --> 00:31:11,289
博科聖地會一直襲擊他們
...Boko Haram will keep attacking them

728
00:31:11,291 --> 00:31:13,124
直到他們全死光
until they're all dead.

729
00:31:14,527 --> 00:31:17,095
你真的能接受嗎
Can you really live with that?

730
