我們現在進退兩難
we're danged if we do and danged if we don't.

750
00:31:56,302 --> 00:31:58,102
如果我們不做點什麼
I mean, if we don't do something,

751
00:31:58,104 --> 00:32:00,972
恐怖分子肯定會搶走槍
the terrorists are gonna get their hands on them guns anyway.

752
00:32:00,974 --> 00:32:02,773
還可能用它們來對付那些
Yeah, and probably use them against the very people

753
00:32:02,775 --> 00:32:03,941
Nadine想要救的人
Nadine's trying to save.

754
00:32:03,943 --> 00:32:05,743
Nadine也知道這個情況
Nadine knows we know that, too,

755
00:32:05,745 --> 00:32:08,012
可能因此希望我們放了她
probably hoping we'll let her go because of it.

756
00:32:08,014 --> 00:32:09,814
真是進退維谷
It's a catch-22.

757
00:32:09,816 --> 00:32:12,049
好了
All right,

758
00:32:12,051 --> 00:32:13,784
我們放她走
we'll let her go.

759
00:32:14,854 --> 00:32:17,522
但要跟著她 讓她帶我們找到槍
But only to follow her so she leads us to the guns.

760
00:32:17,524 --> 00:32:19,257
等等 你是說我們要給她下套嗎
Wait, you mean we're gonna trick her?

761
00:32:19,259 --> 00:32:22,493
不是下套 是要救她
No, not trying to trick her, trying to save her life

762
00:32:22,495 --> 00:32:24,295
同時 不讓博科聖地得到那些槍
and keep Boko Haram from getting those guns.

763
00:32:24,297 --> 00:32:27,798
我們只能幫她到這兒了
And that's gonna have to be enough for you.

764
00:32:28,935 --> 00:32:30,835
明白了嗎
Clear?

765
00:32:45,398 --> 00:32:46,745
