<i>Nadine's still</i> <i>heading east towards</i>

766
00:32:46,746 --> 00:32:48,579
沿著星條大道
<i>Stars and Stripes Boulevard,</i>

767
00:32:48,581 --> 00:32:50,381
時速超過限速15英里
<i>going about 15 miles</i> <i>over the speed limit,</i>

768
00:32:50,383 --> 00:32:52,216
也許你想把這條也加入指控
in case you want to add that to the charges.

769
00:32:52,218 --> 00:32:53,418
她是去機場嗎
Think she's heading to the airport?

770
00:32:53,420 --> 00:32:54,819
希望不是
I hope not,

771
00:32:54,821 --> 00:32:56,287
因為所有光學測距器的單元信號
'cause all the RF and cell signals

772
00:32:56,289 --> 00:32:58,456
都可能破壞你放在她口袋裏的追蹤器
might screw up the geotracker you put in her coat.

773
00:32:58,458 --> 00:32:59,824
全靠你了 Patton
Counting on you, Patton.

774
00:32:59,826 --> 00:33:01,726
我們得離她足夠近才能保護她
We got to stay close enough to protect her

775
00:33:01,728 --> 00:33:02,927
