00:33:02,929 --> 00:33:04,696
但不能太近 防止她發現我們
but not so close that she spots us.

777
00:33:04,698 --> 00:33:06,397
我想知道他們為什麼還沒襲擊她
I wonder why they haven't attacked her yet.

778
00:33:06,399 --> 00:33:07,899
也許他們已經找到槍了
Maybe they already found the guns,

779
00:33:07,901 --> 00:33:09,701
要是這樣的話 他們就不需要跟著她了
and if so, they don't need to follow her.

780
00:33:09,703 --> 00:33:11,135
除非他們一開始就不是衝著槍而來
Except they didn't come for the guns first,

781
00:33:11,137 --> 00:33:12,537
而是衝著Nadine來的
they came for Nadine.

782
00:33:12,539 --> 00:33:15,373
不要擔心 我們會保護她的
Don't worry, we're not gonna let anything happen to her.

783
00:33:15,375 --> 00:33:18,042
記住 一旦她帶我們找到槍
Just remember, as soon as she leads us to the guns,

784
00:33:18,044 --> 00:33:20,244
我們就要逮捕Nadine
we got to get Nadine,

785
00:33:20,246 --> 00:33:22,080
拿到槍 然後離開
get the guns, and then get out of there.

786
00:33:22,082 --> 00:33:23,381
特別是當他們已經找到了槍的情況
Especially if they already found them.

787
00:33:23,383 --> 00:33:25,016
他們可能就在那兒等她
They could be lying in wait for her.

788
00:33:25,018 --> 00:33:26,718
她從Crofton下去了
She's getting off on Crofton.

789
00:33:26,720 --> 00:33:29,053
可能是去出租的飛機棚
She might be headed to the charter hangars.

790
00:33:29,055 --> 00:33:31,255
該死 她的信號中斷了
Damn it, her signal's breaking up.

791
00:33:31,257 --> 00:33:33,358
我們得拉近距離
We got to close the gap.

792
00:33:36,963 --> 00:33:39,497
我不明白這事 Christopher
I don't know about this, Christopher.

793
00:33:39,499 --> 00:33:42,266
我還是不敢相信 我們要逮捕她
I still can't believe we're gonna arrest her.

794
00:33:42,268 --> 00:33:46,104
King做了決定 我們做好自己的工作就行了
King made the call. Let's just do our jobs.

795
00:33:55,548 --> 00:33:57,448
這個集裝箱應該已經卸貨了
The storage pods were supposed to be unloaded

796
00:33:57,450 --> 00:33:59,717
並且已經在飛機上了 我沒法等那麼久
and on the plane by now. I can't wait that long.

797
00:33:59,719 --> 00:34:01,486
對不起 Nadine 但我們得推遲
I'm sorry, Nadine, but we got delayed

798
00:34:01,488 --> 00:34:02,520
到達機場
getting to the airport.

799
00:34:02,522 --> 00:34:04,956
等等 有些不對勁
Wait. Something's happened.

800
00:34:04,958 --> 00:34:06,257
槍在哪兒
Where are the guns?

801
