你什麼意思 什麼槍在哪兒
What do you mean, where are the guns?

802
00:34:08,028 --> 00:34:09,460
Nadine 怎麼了
Nadine, what's wrong?

803
00:34:09,462 --> 00:34:10,895
一切都還好嗎
Is everything okay?

804
00:34:10,897 --> 00:34:12,597
