Nadine, stop!

808
00:34:47,500 --> 00:34:48,499
你跟蹤我
You followed me.

809
00:34:48,501 --> 00:34:50,168
是的 而且又一次救了你的命
Yeah, and saved your life again.

810
00:34:51,271 --> 00:34:53,337
