00:34:53,339 --> 00:34:55,339
博科聖地會為了這事兒報復村民的
Boko Haram's gonna retaliate against the villagers for this.

812
00:34:55,341 --> 00:34:58,709
如果我沒法把槍給他們 至少讓我警示他們
If I can't get them guns, at least let me warn them,

813
00:34:58,711 --> 00:35:00,011
