I have the means.

815
00:35:03,650 --> 00:35:05,750
如果你允許 我可以很快離開這個國家
I can easily leave the country if you let me.

816
00:35:05,752 --> 00:35:07,685
對不起 Nadine 我不能
No, I'm sorry, Nadine, I can't.

817
00:35:07,687 --> 00:35:09,687
拜託了
Please.

818
