Percy 你沒事吧
Percy, you good?

819
00:35:40,687 --> 00:35:42,220
Nadine怎麼樣了
How's Nadine?

820
00:35:46,226 --> 00:35:47,725
她去哪兒了
Where is she?

821
00:35:49,562 --> 00:35:50,962
她 她跑了
Sh-She got away.

822
00:35:50,964 --> 00:35:53,331
陪著他
Stay with him.

823
00:36:04,778 --> 00:36:07,479
我想知道今天外面發生了些什麼
I want to know what happened out there today.

824
00:36:07,481 --> 00:36:09,514
我已經告訴你我知道的了 Pride
I told you what I know, Pride.

825
00:36:09,516 --> 00:36:12,617
你告訴了我 你想讓我知道的
You told me what you want me to know.

826
00:36:12,619 --> 00:36:14,919
Nadine不可能在你手下跑了
No way Nadine got away from you.

827
00:36:15,321 --> 00:36:17,856
見鬼了 Sonja
Damn it, Sonja,

828
00:36:17,858 --> 00:36:21,793
Brody走後 我努力重建這支隊伍
I worked too hard to rebuild this team after Brody left.

829
00:36:21,895 --> 00:36:23,128
比以前更強大了
Stronger than ever.

830
00:36:23,230 --> 00:36:25,831
你怎麼可以冒險把這一切都毀了呢
How could you be so willing to risk throwing it all away?

831
00:36:26,333 --> 00:36:29,751
這個隊伍對你的意義 不比別人少吧
This team means as much, if not more, to you than to anybody.

832
00:36:29,752 --> 00:36:30,666
這知道
I know that.

833
00:36:30,690 --> 00:36:32,650
那你為什麼不告訴我到底發生了什麼
Then why the hell won't you tell me what happened?

834
00:36:33,306 --> 00:36:35,106
有什麼區別呢
What difference does it make?

835
00:36:35,108 --> 00:36:37,075
我們抓到了恐怖分子 對嗎
We got the terrorists, didn't we?

836
00:36:37,077 --> 00:36:38,576
還有槍支
And the guns.

837
00:36:38,578 --> 00:36:40,078
Nadine不是壞人
Nadine is not the bad guy.

838
00:36:40,080 --> 00:36:42,213
那怎麼那麼多執法部門
Then how come half of law enforcement's

839
00:36:42,215 --> 00:36:44,282
仍然在外面找她
still out there looking for her?

840
00:36:48,221 --> 00:36:52,524
如果我告訴你了 Pride 任何這間辦公室之外的人
If I told you, Pride, and anybody outside of this office

841
